Marketing Brief -- Pfizer Inc.:
   Microwave Browning Agent,
   Low-Fat Products Unveiled
Pfizer, which created a special lightfoods marketing unit
last year, said it developed both products while working with
consumers to address their complaints about the taste of
low-fat foods and the relatively colorless look of microwaved
dishes. The company's other products include Litesse, a sugar
and fat substitute for baked goods, confections and frozen
dairy desserts.